ENTRY            A0324   20260124   20260317   20260317       A129
SUBENT        A0324001   20260124   20260317   20260317       A129
BIB                 10         26
TITLE      The E1 capture amplitude in 12-C(alpha,gamma0)16-O
AUTHOR     (L.Gialanella, D.Rogalla, F.Strieder, S.Theis,
           G.Gyurki, C.Agodi, R.Alba, M.Aliotta, L.Campajola,
           A.Del Zoppo, A.D'Onofrio, P.Figuera, U.Greife,
           G.Imbriani, A.Ordine, V.Roca, C.Rolfs, M.Romano,
           C.Sabbarese, P.Sapienza, F.Schuemann, E.Somorjai,
           F.Terrasi, H.P.Trautvetter)
REFERENCE  (J,EPJ/A,11,357,2001)
INSTITUTE  (2GERBOC,2ITYNAP,2ITYFSN,2ITYLNS,3HUNDEB)
FACILITY   (DYNAM,2GERBOC)
SAMPLE     A windowless gas target.
DETECTOR   (GE) 6 coaxial Ge detectors to detect gamma - rays.
           (PROPC) A 3He proportional counter was placed near
           the gas cell and monitored the neutron flux in the
           detector region.
           (SIBAR) To detect elastically scattered He-4. A Si
           surface-barrier detector (100 um thickness) installed
           at 75. degr. in the gas cell.
METHOD     (SITA,GSPEC,BCINT)
ADD-RES    The data at E = 1.32 to 2.99 MeV lead to an
           extrapolated astrophysical S factor
           SE1(E0) = 90 +-15 (keV x b) at E0 = 0.3 MeV.
HISTORY    (20020617C)
           (20021217U) Last checking has been done.
           (20260124A) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           MISC deleted (data moved to col. E-EXC-CMP).
ENDBIB              26
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           29
SUBENT        A0324002   20260124   20260317   20260317       A129
BIB                  7         14
REACTION   (2-HE-4(6-C-12,EL)2-HE-4,,DA,,RTH)
MONITOR    (18-AR-0(6-C-12,EL)18-AR-0,,DA,,RTH)
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical error
COMMENT    - By authors: the results have been normalised to the
           Rutherford scattering cross-section at the lowest
           energies, where the intensity ratio approached a
           constant value. The data are in good agreement with
           previous works.
REL-REF    (A,A0652002,G.Roters+,J,EPJ/A,6,451,1999)
           (A,,K.U.Kettner+,J,ZP/A,308,73,1982)
STATUS     (TABLE,,L.Gialanella+,J,EPJ/A,11,357,2001) Tbl.1
HISTORY    (20260124A) SD: STATUS added. DATA-ERR -> ERR-S.
           MISC -> E-EXC-CMP. Col.EN deleted (calculated by
           compiler).
ENDBIB              14
COMMON               2          3
ANG        ANG-ERR
ADEG       ADEG
        75.        0.3
ENDCOMMON            3
