SUBENT        A0324003   20260124   20260317   20260317       A129
BIB                  6         13
REACTION   (2-HE-4(6-C-12,G)8-O-16,EP,SIG,,SFC)
REL-REF    (R,,H.W.Becker+,J,ZP/A,305,319,1982) Cross section of
            1-H-1(9-F-19,gamma+alpha)8-O-16 at 6453 keV.
FLAG       (1.) Absolute value measured relative to
            1-H(F-19,gamma+alpha)16-O with a normalisation error
           of 9%, which is common to all data points
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) The quoted uncertainties represent statistical
           errors on the relative yield curve only.
           (ERR-1) Normalization error
STATUS     (TABLE,,L.Gialanella+,J,EPJ/A,11,357,2001) Tbl.2
HISTORY    (20260124A) SD: STATUS added.  MISC -> E-EXC-CMP.
           Col.EN deleted (calculated by compiler).
           E-LVL-FIN -> E-LVL.
ENDBIB              13
